Terrorists have infiltraited a ammo factory and are preparing to blow it up. Its at night, only a few lights are on so it's kinda dark in there. Factory is set up like a maze of work areas with two doors each, you can be seen from everywhere.

medium sized area, warehouse, work areas, hallways and office
